data.eml:eml: Primnoidae (Cnidaria: Octocorallia: Calcaxonia) of the Okeanos Explorer expeditions (CAPSTONE) to the central Pacific

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Cairns, Stephen D. (2018): Primnoidae (Cnidaria: Octocorallia: Calcaxonia) of the Okeanos Explorer expeditions (CAPSTONE) to the central Pacific. Zootaxa 4532 (1): 1-43, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4532.1.1
